ed="T" n="0798a21"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0798a21"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>會稽開元寺<persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0798a22"/><persName key="A004177">釋曇一</persName><ptr target="#n415"/>，姓張氏，蓋<placeName key="PL000000023246">韓</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n1486"/>。其先<persName key="A004009">軒轅</persName>賦姓，<lb
ed="T" n="0798a23"/>至<persName key="A003195">良</persName>佐<placeName key="PL000000000097">漢</placeName>，侯于<placeName key="PL000000009592">留</placeName>。魏晉已還，衣冠繼代。<anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>僧</sic><corr>曾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz2"/><lb
ed="T" n="0798a24"/>祖<persName key="A010924">恒</persName>隋太常卿，扈蹕<placeName key="PL000000010783"><anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz3"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz3"/>都</placeName>，遂家<anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz4"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz4"/><placeName key="PL000000000197">越</placeName>。<persName key="A010924">恒</persName>生<lb
ed="T" n="0798a25"/>孝廉<persName key="A010925">翼</persName>，<persName key="A010925">翼</persName>生處士<persName key="A010926">蕆</persName>，<persName key="A010926">蕆</persName>生<persName key="A004177">一</persName>，令聞<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>，今<lb
ed="T" n="0798a26"/>四葉矣。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>宿植淨因，生知慧性，弱而敏悟，長<lb
ed="T" n="0798a27"/>而聰明。<date key="j19789211979285" from-iso="+0706-01-01" to-iso="+0706-12-31">年十五</date>，從<persName key="A010927">李滔先生</persName>習《詩》《禮》，終日<lb
ed="T" n="0798a28"/>不違。<date key="j19792861979650" from-iso="+0707-01-01" to-iso="+0707-12-31">十六</date>，聽<placeName key="PL000000013295">雲門寺</placeName><persName key="A010928">茂亮<roleName>法師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n418"/>經論，<persName key="A004177">一</persName>聞懸<lb
ed="T" n="0798a29"/>解。<persName key="A010928">法師</persName>異之，謂其母<persName key="A019338">孟<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>曰：「此佛子也，可<pb ed="T" n="0798b" xml:id="T50.2061.0798b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0798b01"/>令削髮，當與授記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1351"/>。」<persName key="A010928">亮</persName>即<persName key="A002100">孝和皇帝</persName>菩薩戒<lb
ed="T" n="0798b02"/>師也。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>聞而歡喜，有度世之志。<date notBefore-iso="+0707-10-09" key="j19795671980570" notAfter-iso="+0710-07-08"><name>景龍</name>中</date>，承恩<lb
ed="T" n="0798b03"/>出家，隷在僧錄。年滿受具於<placeName key="PL000000010986">丹陽</placeName><persName key="A010929">玄昶律<lb
ed="T" n="0798b04"/>師</persName>，學通《事鈔》於<placeName key="PL000000027041">當陽</placeName><persName key="A010930">曇勝律師</persName>。既而鑽木見<lb
ed="T" n="0798b05"/>煙，窺牆覩奧。<date from-iso="+0717-02-20" key="j19829891983342" to-iso="+0718-02-08"><name>開元</name>五年</date>，西遊<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，依<placeName key="PL000000042420">觀音<lb
ed="T" n="0798b06"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A010825">大亮律師</persName>，傳《毘尼藏》，崇聖寺<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A010931">檀子<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>學<lb
ed="T" n="0798b07"/>《唯識》、《俱舍》等論，<placeName key="PL000000042180">安國寺</placeName><placeName key="PL000000048207">印度</placeName>沙門受菩薩戒<ptr target="#n419"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0798b08"/>於是蓮<anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz5"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz5"/>不染之義，甘露甚深之旨，<persName key="A004177">一</persName>傳慧<lb
ed="T" n="0798b09"/>炬，了作<name>梵</name>雄。遠近瞻仰，如宗師矣。然刃有<lb
ed="T" n="0798b10"/>餘地，時兼外學，常問《周易》於左常侍<persName key="A010934">禇無<lb
ed="T" n="0798b11"/>量</persName>，論《史記》於國子<persName key="A010935">司業馬貞</persName><ptr target="#n1154"/>。遂漁獵百氏，<lb
ed="T" n="0798b12"/>囊括《六籍》，增廣聞見，自是儒家，調御人天，<lb
ed="T" n="0798b13"/>皆因佛事。公卿<anchor xml:id="beg0798001"/>嚮<anchor xml:id="end0798001"/>慕，<placeName key="PL000000042189">京師</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz7"/>籍<anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz7"/>甚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g691"/>。時丞相燕<lb
ed="T" n="0798b14"/>國公<persName key="A002473">張說</persName>、廣平<persName key="A010074">宋璟</persName>、尚書<persName key="A002476">蘇瓌</persName>、兗國<persName key="A009070">陸象先</persName>、祕<lb
ed="T" n="0798b15"/>書監<persName key="A008710">賀知章</persName>、宣州<placeName key="PL000000017029">涇縣</placeName>令<persName key="A007959">萬齊融</persName>、皆以同聲<lb
ed="T" n="0798b16"/>並為師友，雖<persName key="A002205">支</persName><persName key="A002695">許</persName>之會<placeName key="PL000000013174"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>虛</sic><corr>靈</corr></choice>嘉</placeName><ptr target="#n420"/>，<persName key="A002812">宗</persName><persName key="A002810">雷</persName>之集廬<lb
ed="T" n="0798b17"/>岳，未云多也。《四分律》者，後秦三藏法師<name>梵</name>僧<lb
ed="T" n="0798b18"/><persName key="A000439">佛陀耶舍</persName>傳誦中華，與<persName key="A001583">羅什法師</persName>共為翻<lb
ed="T" n="0798b19"/>譯，今之講授，自此員來。魏<persName key="A007009">法聰律師</persName>始為演<lb
ed="T" n="0798b20"/>說，<persName key="A007009">聰</persName>授<persName key="A006355">道覆</persName>，<persName key="A006355">覆</persName>授<persName key="A006354">光</persName>。洎隋朝相部<persName key="A000747">勵律師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0798b21"/>作《疏》十卷，西京<placeName key="PL000000042324">崇福寺</placeName><persName key="A010776">滿意律師</persName>盛傳此《疏》，<lb
ed="T" n="0798b22"/>付授<persName key="A010825">亮律師</persName>。其所傳授<persName key="A004177">一</persName>，<persName key="A004177">一</persName>依<persName key="A000747">勵律師</persName>疏<lb
ed="T" n="0798b23"/>及唐初<placeName key="PL000000042627">終南</placeName><persName key="A001519">宣律師</persName>《四分律鈔》三卷，詳略同<lb
ed="T" n="0798b24"/>異。自著《發正義記》十卷。明兩宗之踳駁<ptr type="glossary" target="#g71"/>，發<lb
ed="T" n="0798b25"/>五部之鈐鍵。後學開悟，夜行得燭，前疑泮釋，<lb
ed="T" n="0798b26"/>陽和解氷，佛日昭<anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz11"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>晰</sic><corr>晣</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz11"/>而再中，法棟崢嶸以高<lb
ed="T" n="0798b27"/>峙，《發正記》中斥破<ref type="person" target="#A001519">南山</ref>持犯中可見也。<date from-iso="+0737-02-08" key="j19902821990636" to-iso="+0738-01-28">二<lb
ed="T" n="0798b28"/>十五年</date>，仗錫東歸。<date from-iso="+0738-01-29" key="j19906371991020" to-iso="+0739-02-16">明年</date>詔置開元寺，長史<persName key="A010954">張<lb
ed="T" n="0798b29"/>楚</persName>舉為<placeName key="PL000000013226">寺</placeName>主，因而居焉<ptr target="#n421"/>。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>聲振<placeName key="PL000000042189">京華</placeName>，道高<pb ed="T" n="0798c" xml:id="T50.2061.0798c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0798c01"/>吳會，布大慈以攝眾，修萬行以表儀。順<lb
ed="T" n="0798c02"/>風問道者轂擊肩摩，函丈請益者波委雲<lb
ed="T" n="0798c03"/>萃。虛受之量，隨而演說，故前後講《四分律》三<lb
ed="T" n="0798c04"/>十五遍，《刪補鈔》二十餘遍焉。<placeName key="PL000000015039">江淮</placeName>釋子受木<lb
ed="T" n="0798c05"/>叉者，非<persName key="A004177">一</persName>登壇即不為得法。從持僧律，<lb
ed="T" n="0798c06"/>蓋度人十萬計矣。<date from-iso="+0756-08-16" key="j19974111997993" to-iso="+0758-03-21"><name>至德</name></date>之際，國步多艱，緇徒<lb
ed="T" n="0798c07"/>慢法，罕率經教。國相<ref type="person" target="#A019339">王公</ref>出鎮<anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz13"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz13"/><placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>，以<persName key="A004177">一</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0798c08"/>德名素高，請為僧統。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>變清淨，大闡熏修，<lb
ed="T" n="0798c09"/>浹旬之間，迴邪入正。善誘潛化，皆此類焉。始<lb
ed="T" n="0798c10"/>者<persName key="A004177">一</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000042002">關</placeName>謁<persName key="A010941">明達<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>，目之曰：「汝人中師<lb
ed="T" n="0798c11"/>子也。」又遇<placeName key="PL000000042218">遵善寺</placeName>尼<persName key="A010942">慈和</persName>，歌曰：「<persName key="A004177">曇一師</persName>，解<lb
ed="T" n="0798c12"/>毘尼，大聰明，更無疑。」為達人之所諺多矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0798c13"/><date from-iso="+0755-02-20" key="j19968681997221" to-iso="+0756-02-08"><name>天寶</name>十四載</date>，<placeName key="PL000000008367">淛河</placeName>潮水南激<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000011481">大雲伽藍</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0798c14"/>當茲湍𣵡，因請<persName key="A004177">一</persName>講律，學徒千人咸發大<lb
ed="T" n="0798c15"/>願。每上，念摩訶般若，乃止濤激，以福<persName key="A010943">伍胥</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0798c16"/>龍王。用茲莊嚴，祈於衛護。<date from-iso="+0755-06-18" key="j19969861997015" to-iso="+0755-07-17">五月</date>晦夜，惚怳<lb
ed="T" n="0798c17"/>之間，見一神人，衣冠甚偉，稽首謝曰：「蒙垂<lb
ed="T" n="0798c18"/>法施，即改波流。」未逾九十日，漲沙五十里，<lb
ed="T" n="0798c19"/>道俗驚歎，得未曾有。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>蔚為法主，大揚教<lb
ed="T" n="0798c20"/>跡，發明前佛之付囑，保證後佛之護念。四<lb
ed="T" n="0798c21"/>句作偈，受持者了於未了；一音演法，諦聽者<lb
ed="T" n="0798c22"/>聞所不聞。非夫天地淳精，江山粹靈，與法<lb
ed="T" n="0798c23"/>作程，間世而生。孰能玄通密證如此其大者<lb
ed="T" n="0798c24"/>乎？寺中洪鐘，<persName key="A004177">一</persName>所作也，遠徵鳧氏，近法雷<lb
ed="T" n="0798c25"/>門。生存累年，匠其規制，歿後三日，成於鎔造，<lb
ed="T" n="0798c26"/>聲應百里，扛乎萬鈞，蒲牢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g43"/>叫而地震，師子<lb
ed="T" n="0798c27"/>吼而山嶪，警悟聾俗，導引迷方，胡可言也！<lb
ed="T" n="0798c28"/>法謝形離，薪盡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g152"/>火滅，以<date key="j20030262003026" when-iso="+0771-12-31"><name>大曆</name>六年十一月十<lb
ed="T" n="0798c29"/>七日</date><ptr target="#n422"/>遷化於寺之律院，報齡八十，僧臘六十<pb ed="T" n="0799a" xml:id="T50.2061.0799a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0799a01"/>一。即以<date key="j20033872003387" when-iso="+0772-12-26">明年十一月二十四日</date>遷座於<placeName key="PL000000013158">秦望<lb
ed="T" n="0799a02"/>山</placeName>，從先和尚之塋也。<persName key="A004177">一</persName>春秋已高，精爽逾<lb
ed="T" n="0799a03"/>勵，既不衰憊，初無疾苦。忽謂侍者曰：「<persName key="A004177">吾</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0799a04"/>將掃禮墳塔，歸骨於此。」數日之後，奄然而<lb
ed="T" n="0799a05"/>終。<placeName key="PL000000015039">江淮</placeName>之南，<placeName key="PL000000000214">河洛</placeName>之表，衣縗制服，執紼送<lb
ed="T" n="0799a06"/>喪，號哭滿山，旛<anchor xml:id="beg0799sgsz1"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0799sgsz1"/>蔽野，比夫<persName key="A019340">劇孟</persName>之母送<lb
ed="T" n="0799a07"/>車千乘，<persName key="A002174">孔丘</persName>之墓<anchor xml:id="beg0799001"/>栽<anchor xml:id="end0799001"/>樹萬株，可同年哉！門<lb
ed="T" n="0799a08"/>人越州<placeName key="PL000000013294">妙喜寺</placeName><persName key="A010042">常照</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013232">建法寺</placeName><persName key="A010904">清源</persName>、湖州<placeName key="PL000000012986">龍興寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0799a09"/><persName key="A010947">神玩</persName>、宣州<placeName key="PL000000016942">隱靜寺</placeName><persName key="A010948">道昂</persName>、杭州<placeName key="PL000000011473">龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A010527">義賓</persName>、台州<lb
ed="T" n="0799a10"/><placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName><persName key="A001307">湛然</persName>、蘇州<placeName key="PL000000009882">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A010899">辯秀</persName>、潤州<placeName key="PL000000009026">棲霞寺</placeName><persName key="A010951">昭<lb
ed="T" n="0799a11"/>亮</persName>、常州<placeName key="PL000000009711">龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A010953">法俊</persName>等，早發童蒙，咸承訓<lb
ed="T" n="0799a12"/>誘，三千弟子仰梁木而增悲，八萬門人望<lb
ed="T" n="0799a13"/>栴檀而不及。時<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName><persName key="A008847">徐公浩</persName>素敦鄉里之<lb
ed="T" n="0799a14"/>舊，為碑頌德焉。<date from-iso="+0776-01-30" key="j20045172004900" to-iso="+0777-02-16"><name>大曆</name>十一年</date>也。</p>
